<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>Cosmo Duel is a galactic combat strategy game developed by MyDreams. Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains what data Cosmo Duel collects — and more importantly, what it does <strong>not</strong> collect.</p>

<h2>Data Collection</h2>
<p>Cosmo Duel does <strong>not</strong> collect, transmit, or share any personal data. Specifically:</p>
<ul>
  <li>No account or registration is required.</li>
  <li>No personal information is ever collected.</li>
  <li>No usage data, analytics, or telemetry is sent to any server.</li>
  <li>No advertising network or third-party SDK is included.</li>
  <li>The app does not require an internet connection.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Local Storage</h2>
<p>Cosmo Duel stores your game settings (grid size, number of drones, etc.) as well as the number of wins/defeats locally on your device using Android's standard storage mechanisms. This data never leaves your device and can be cleared at any time by uninstalling the app.</p>

<h2>Permissions</h2>
<p>Cosmo Duel does not request any sensitive permissions (camera, microphone, location, contacts, etc.).</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Cosmo Duel does not knowingly collect data from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>If this policy is updated, the new version will be published at this URL with an updated date.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you may contact us at the email address listed on the Google Play Store page.</p>
